2/2140 Clearance Confirmed

The glyph image is by Petrograd. He used fonts by Juan Carlos Porcel from http://elderprops.tumblr.com/post/89934858272/free-fonts-necrofonticon2. All under CC.

The deep storage facility is Svalbard seed vault IMG 8887 by Bjoertvedt also CC.

Word count as of posting: 492.

I was vaguely inspired by GURPS Horror: The Madness Dossier  by Kenneth Hite.

Thanks to Mr. Wrong, Eta Carinae, and especially psul and Petrograd for review!

Edit: Kallinikos was the guy who brought Greek Fire to Byzantium and oversaw the first known compartmentalized development of a weapon system.





